Class MessMoveCharacterAnswer

    • pp2016.team19.shared.Message

    public class MessMoveCharacterAnswer
extends Message
implements java.io.Serializable

    This class presents the MoveCharacterAnswer Message from the server.

    Move Character Answer from server. This message determines the position of the player. It contains the constructor as well as a getter and setter methods.
    Author:
